{
  "texts": [
    "The set M includes DT, RF, SVM, k-NN, and ANN.",
    "Each individual machine learning model in M is represented as M i, where 'i' is a subscript that ranges from 1 to the total number of models.",
    "The weights assigned to each model Mi for combining their predictions are represented by W i.",
    "The Ensemble Federated Learning component of the system is represented by EFL(D, M).",
    "The Online Anomaly Detection with Energy-Efficient Techniques component of the system is represented by OAD_EE(D, M)."
  ]
}